ActCanada Council for the Arts Act
PrecisAppointment of KIM SPENCER-NAIRN of Vancouver, British Columbia, to be a member of the Canada Council for the Arts, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, effective October 30, 2018, in the place of Cheryl Ann Sharfe, whose term will expire.
